Will it be
Yes, it will

263
00:27:52,141 --> 00:27:54,727
Maybe just by holdin' still

264
00:27:54,811 --> 00:27:57,272
lt'll be there

265
00:27:57,313 --> 00:28:00,566
Come on, somethin'
Come on in, don't be shy

266
00:28:00,650 --> 00:28:04,612
Meet a guy
Pull up a chair

267
00:28:04,696 --> 00:28:09,826
The air is hummin'

