275
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:56,873
One inch. How much
can one little inch do?

276
00:28:56,956 --> 00:28:58,583
Too much.

277
00:28:58,666 --> 00:29:02,545
Anita, it is now to be a dress
for dancing, no longer for praying.

278
