Bernardo made me promise.

281
00:29:14,474 --> 00:29:17,852
One month have l been in this country.
Do l ever even touch excitement?

282
00:29:17,936 --> 00:29:20,688
l sew in this place all day.
l sit at home all night.

283
00:29:20,772 --> 00:29:22,523
For what did my brother
bring me here?

284
00:29:23,524 --> 00:29:25,068
To marry Chino.

285
00:29:26,194 --> 00:29:28,112
When l look at Chino,
nothing happens.

286
00:29:28,196 --> 00:29:30,657
What do you expect to happen?

287
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:33,368
l don't know. Something.

288
00:29:35,245 --> 00:29:37,163
What happens when you
look at Bernardo?

289
00:29:38,331 --> 00:29:41,459
lt's when l don't look
that it happens.

290
00:29:44,796 --> 00:29:47,006
l think l will tell
Mama and Papa...

291
00:29:47,090 --> 00:29:50,385
about you and Nardo
in the balcony of the movies.

292
00:29:50,468 --> 00:29:53,221
- l will rip this to shreds!
- No.

293
00:29:53,304 --> 00:29:56,224
But if you could perhaps manage
to lower the neck.

294
00:29:57,850 --> 00:29:59,978
Next year.

295
00:30:00,061 --> 00:30:02,438
- l hate that dress!
- Then don't wear it.

296
