- Could we not dye it red, at least?
- No, we could not.

299
00:30:15,285 --> 00:30:17,662
White is for babies.

300
00:30:17,745 --> 00:30:21,249
l will be the only one there
in a white--

301
00:30:32,885 --> 00:30:35,221
lt is a beautiful dress.

302
00:30:35,305 --> 00:30:37,599
l love you!

303
00:30:38,808 --> 00:30:41,019
- Are you ready, ladies?
- Nardo, come in.

304
00:30:41,102 --> 00:30:43,605
ls it not beautiful?

305
00:30:43,688 --> 00:30:46,149
Yes. Very.

306
00:30:46,232 --> 00:30:48,693
l didn't quite hear.

307
00:30:48,776 --> 00:30:50,695
Very beautiful.

308
00:30:52,155 --> 00:30:54,365
Come in, Chino.
Do not be afraid.

309
00:30:54,449 --> 00:30:55,909
But this is a shop for ladies.

310
00:30:55,950 --> 00:30:59,913
We won't bite you
till we know you better.

311
00:30:59,954 --> 00:31:03,124
You will keep both eyes on Maria
tonight in case l cannot.

312
00:31:03,166 --> 00:31:05,877
- You too, Anita.
- My brother is a silly watchdog.

313
00:31:05,960 --> 00:31:08,755
My sister is a precious jewel.

314
00:31:10,048 --> 00:31:12,342
What am l, cut glass?

315
00:31:13,843 --> 00:31:18,806
Nardo, it is most important that l have
a wonderful time at the dance tonight.

316
00:31:18,973 --> 00:31:19,641
lt is?

317
00:31:19,724 --> 00:31:22,352
Because tonight is
the real beginning of my life...

318
00:31:22,435 --> 00:31:25,021
as a young lady of America.

319
00:32:29,877 --> 00:32:31,170
Get out of here.

320
00:33:06,789 --> 00:33:08,708
Come on, guys.

321
00:33:13,421 --> 00:33:15,715
- Hey, look what l got.
- Hi, Consuelo.

322
00:33:15,798 --> 00:33:18,176
Maria, these are some of my friends
you have not met.

323
00:33:18,259 --> 00:33:21,262
- Hey, pick up.
- How are you?

324
00:33:21,304 --> 00:33:23,681
This is Loco.

325
00:33:23,723 --> 00:33:25,433
Teresita.

326
00:33:25,516 --> 00:33:26,851
- My sister Maria.
- Good evening.

327
00:33:26,935 --> 00:33:29,312
And this is Luis Arruza.

328
00:33:29,354 --> 00:33:30,813
Rosalia, hi.

329
00:33:41,241 --> 00:33:44,744
All right, boys and girls.

330
00:33:44,786 --> 00:33:46,704
Attention, please.

331
00:33:53,127 --> 00:33:55,922
- Come here.
- Okay, let's get on with it.

332
00:33:56,005 --> 00:33:58,841
My, this is a fine turnout
we have here tonight.

333
00:33:58,925 --> 00:34:01,052
Hey, it's all for you, Glad Hand.

334
00:34:02,553 --> 00:34:05,098
l know all of you
boys and girls are here...

335
00:34:05,181 --> 00:34:07,350
because you want to
make new friends...

336
00:34:07,392 --> 00:34:10,478
and get closer to old ones.

337
00:34:12,272 --> 00:34:13,773
So tonight...

338
00:34:13,856 --> 00:34:16,943
kids, we're gonna do
something special.

339
00:34:17,026 --> 00:34:19,529
We're gonna have
a get-together dance.

340
00:34:19,612 --> 00:34:21,531
Ginger-peachy!

341
00:34:23,283 --> 00:34:25,868
All right. Now, kids.

342
00:34:25,952 --> 00:34:28,621
l want you to form two circles.

343
00:34:28,663 --> 00:34:31,332
- How many?
- Two. Boys on the outside.

344
00:34:31,416 --> 00:34:34,377
- Girls on the inside.
- Hey, where are you?

345
00:34:36,754 --> 00:34:38,172
All right.

346
00:34:40,091 --> 00:34:42,552
When the music stops...

347
00:34:42,635 --> 00:34:46,556
each boy dances with
whichever girl is opposite.

348
00:34:46,598 --> 00:34:47,724
Okay?

349
00:34:49,767 --> 00:34:51,686
Two circles, kids.

350
00:34:56,024 --> 00:34:58,026
Well, it won't hurt you to try.

351
00:34:58,067 --> 00:35:00,945
Ooh, it hurts, it hurts.

352
00:35:01,029 --> 00:35:02,488
Snowboy.

353
00:35:46,574 --> 00:35:49,535
That's it, kids.
Keep the ball rolling.

354
00:35:49,619 --> 00:35:52,497
Around she goes,
and where she stops...

355
00:35:52,580 --> 00:35:54,666
nobody knows.

356
00:35:54,749 --> 00:35:56,626
Here we go.

357
00:35:58,586 --> 00:36:01,673
Boys to my right,
and girls to my left.

358
00:36:32,370 --> 00:36:33,997
- Mambo!
- Mambo!

359
00:36:34,080 --> 00:36:35,832
Go!

360
00:40:33,319 --> 00:40:35,863
You're not thinkin'
l'm someone else?

361
00:40:36,948 --> 00:40:38,866
l know you are not.

362
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:44,247
Or that we met before?

363
00:40:45,915 --> 00:40:47,917
l know we have not.

364
00:40:49,085 --> 00:40:51,337
l felt...

365
00:40:51,379 --> 00:40:53,506
l knew something never before
was going to happen...

366
00:40:53,548 --> 00:40:55,550
had to happen,
but this is so much more.

367
00:40:55,633 --> 00:40:57,594
My hands are cold.

368
00:41:02,348 --> 00:41:04,267
Yours too.

369
00:41:11,316 --> 00:41:12,775
So warm.

370
00:41:18,531 --> 00:41:21,409
So beautiful.

371
00:41:21,492 --> 00:41:22,911
Beautiful.

372
00:41:29,792 --> 00:41:31,961
lt's so much to believe.

373
00:41:33,379 --> 00:41:34,797
You're not makin' a joke.

374
00:41:37,216 --> 00:41:40,178
l have not yet learned
how to joke that way.

375
00:41:41,387 --> 00:41:44,015
l think now l never will.

376
00:42:19,050 --> 00:42:21,135
Get your hands off, American!

377
00:42:21,177 --> 00:42:23,012
- Stay away from my sister.
- Sister?

378
00:42:23,096 --> 00:42:25,473
- Couldn't you see he's one of them?
- No, l saw only him.

379
00:42:25,515 --> 00:42:27,600
There's only one thing they want
from a Puerto Rican girl.

380
00:42:27,684 --> 00:42:29,477
- That's a lie.
- Later, Tony.

381
00:42:29,560 --> 00:42:30,812
Don't listen to them.

382
00:42:30,895 --> 00:42:32,814
She will listen to her brother
before she listens to you.

383
00:42:32,897 --> 00:42:35,233
- lf you two want to settle this--
- Please, boys!

384
00:42:35,316 --> 00:42:39,195
Everything was going so well.
We're all here to have a good time.

385
00:42:39,279 --> 00:42:42,156
Come here a second.
l want to talk to you.

386
00:42:46,869 --> 00:42:49,247
Take her out of here.
We're going home.

387
00:42:49,289 --> 00:42:52,834
- lt is my first dance.
- Please, we are family. Now, go.

388
00:43:03,928 --> 00:43:05,847
Come, Maria.

389
00:43:18,443 --> 00:43:21,613
- l don't want you.
- l want you though.

390
00:43:31,164 --> 00:43:33,875
l want you for a war council.
Jets and Sharks.

391
00:43:34,918 --> 00:43:37,962
- The pleasure is mine.
- Let's go outside.

392
00:43:38,046 --> 00:43:41,007
l would not leave the ladies alone
with your kind around.

393
00:43:41,090 --> 00:43:43,885
We will meet you at midnight.

394
00:43:43,968 --> 00:43:46,304
- Doc's candy store?
- Mm-hmm.

395
00:43:46,387 --> 00:43:47,931
And no jazz before then.

396
00:43:49,015 --> 00:43:51,601
l understand the rules...

397
00:43:51,684 --> 00:43:52,852
native boy.

398
00:43:54,729 --> 00:43:56,147
lce.

399
00:44:01,069 --> 00:44:02,987
Doc's at midnight.
Spread the word.

400
00:44:03,071 --> 00:44:04,530
Right, Daddy-O.

401
00:44:16,960 --> 00:44:22,423
The most beautiful sound
l ever heard

402
00:44:22,507 --> 00:44:24,550
Maria

403
00:44:30,515 --> 00:44:33,351
All the beautiful sounds
of the world

404
00:44:33,434 --> 00:44:36,688
ln a single word

405
00:44:47,198 --> 00:44:51,369
l just met a girl named Maria

406
00:44:51,452 --> 00:44:53,621
And suddenly that name

407
00:44:53,705 --> 00:44:57,709
Will never be the same to me

408
00:44:59,877 --> 00:45:03,840
l just kissed a girl
named Maria

409
00:45:03,881 --> 00:45:06,134
And suddenly l found

410
00:45:06,175 --> 00:45:09,929
How wonderful a sound can be

411
00:45:12,223 --> 00:45:17,687
Say it loud
and there's music playing

412
00:45:17,770 --> 00:45:19,772
Say it soft

413
00:45:19,856 --> 00:45:23,776
And it's almost like praying

414
00:45:26,487 --> 00:45:29,157
l'll never stop saying

415
00:45:56,643 --> 00:46:01,522
Say it loud
and there's music playing

416
00:46:01,606 --> 00:46:03,691
Say it soft

417
00:46:03,775 --> 00:46:07,820
