00:46:25,296 --> 00:46:28,049
The most beautiful sound

420
00:46:28,132 --> 00:46:32,262
l ever heard

421
00:46:48,945 --> 00:46:51,656
Now, l do not say these things
to spoil your evening...

422
00:46:51,698 --> 00:46:53,366
or to hear myself talk.

423
00:46:53,449 --> 00:46:55,577
l am here longer than you.

424
00:46:55,618 --> 00:46:58,621
Someday when you are an old
married woman with five children...

425
00:46:58,705 --> 00:47:02,542
then you can tell me what to do,
but now it is the other way around.

426
00:47:02,584 --> 00:47:04,877
Now go to bed.

427
00:47:04,961 --> 00:47:07,255
He's the old married woman.

428
00:47:13,094 --> 00:47:16,014
You know, she has a mother,
also a father.

429
00:47:16,055 --> 00:47:18,224
They do not know this country
any better than she does.

430
00:47:18,308 --> 00:47:19,892
You do not know it at all.

431
00:47:19,976 --> 00:47:24,063
Girls here are free to have fun.
She is in America now.

432
00:47:24,147 --> 00:47:26,900
Puerto Rico is in America now.

433
00:47:30,028 --> 00:47:32,196
Sometimes l don't know
which is thicker--

434
00:47:32,280 --> 00:47:34,741
your skull or your accent.

435
00:47:40,788 --> 00:47:42,957
- Let them wait.
- ls Maria all right?

436
00:47:43,041 --> 00:47:45,835
- l should be so all right.
