437
00:47:45,919 --> 00:47:47,587
Pepe, lndio.

438
00:47:47,670 --> 00:47:50,840
- After tonight, things will be settled.
- First settle your stomach.

439
00:47:50,924 --> 00:47:52,175
Never mind my stomach.

440
00:47:52,216 --> 00:47:55,929
Well, l mind your nose
and your head broken.

441
00:47:56,012 --> 00:47:57,680
- Broken?
- Sure.

442
00:47:57,764 --> 00:48:00,141
They use Maria for an excuse
to start World War lll.

