00:50:23,117 --> 00:50:25,453
l like to be in America

496
00:50:25,536 --> 00:50:27,789
Okay by me in America

497
00:50:27,830 --> 00:50:29,999
Everything free in America

498
00:50:30,083 --> 00:50:33,253
For a small fee in America

499
00:50:36,881 --> 00:50:39,217
Buying on credit is so nice

