02:16:30,347 --> 02:16:32,558
-Don't let her go!
-She'll tell Chino Tony's in the cellar!

1488
02:16:32,641 --> 02:16:34,601
Don't you touch me.

1489
02:16:37,646 --> 02:16:41,567
l got a message
for your American buddy.

1490
02:16:41,650 --> 02:16:43,569
You tell that murderer...

1491
02:16:43,652 --> 02:16:46,280
that Maria's
never going to meet him.

1492
02:16:46,363 --> 02:16:50,200
You tell him that Chino
found out about them...

1493
02:16:50,284 --> 02:16:52,077
and shot her!

1494
02:16:53,120 --> 02:16:54,872
She's dead.

1495
02:16:59,001 --> 02:17:02,129
When do you kids stop?

1496
02:17:02,171 --> 02:17:05,799
You make this world lousy.

1497
02:17:05,883 --> 02:17:07,968
We didn't make it, Doc.

1498
02:17:09,803 --> 02:17:11,847
Get outta here.

1499
02:17:43,712 --> 02:17:46,465
Doc, l thought l heard--
You got it!

1500
02:17:46,548 --> 02:17:49,051
Yeah, l got it.

1501
02:17:49,134 --> 02:17:52,304
You're a pal.
You're the best friend a guy ever had.

1502
02:17:52,388 --> 02:17:54,932
l'll pay you back
as soon as l can, l promise.

1503
02:17:54,974 --> 02:17:58,060
- Forget that.
- Never. l couldn't.

1504
02:17:58,143 --> 02:18:01,355
Doc, you know what we're gonna do
in the country, Maria and me?

1505
02:18:01,438 --> 02:18:04,108
We're gonna have lots of kids,
and we're gonna name 'em after ya.

1506
02:18:04,191 --> 02:18:06,193
That way,
when you come to visit us--

1507
02:18:06,276 --> 02:18:07,653
Wake up!

1508
02:18:08,654 --> 02:18:12,116
ls this the only way
to get through to you?

1509
02:18:12,199 --> 02:18:16,453
Do just what you all do?
Bust like a hot water pipe?

1510
02:18:16,495 --> 02:18:17,997
What's got into you?

1511
02:18:18,080 --> 02:18:21,709
Why do you kids live
like there's a war on?

1512
02:18:26,088 --> 02:18:28,007
Why do you kill?

1513
02:18:31,760 --> 02:18:34,013
l told you how it happened.

1514
02:18:35,264 --> 02:18:37,474
Maria understands.

1515
02:18:37,558 --> 02:18:39,268
l thought you did too.

1516
02:18:39,351 --> 02:18:42,563
Maria understands nothing...

1517
02:18:42,646 --> 02:18:44,356
ever again.

1518
02:18:44,440 --> 02:18:46,859
There is no Maria, Tony.

1519
02:18:50,654 --> 02:18:51,572
What?

1520
02:18:53,407 --> 02:18:56,285
- l can't.
- No, Doc!

1521
02:18:56,327 --> 02:18:58,620
Now tell me!
What is it?

1522
02:18:59,663 --> 02:19:02,708
That was Anita upstairs.

1523
02:19:02,791 --> 02:19:05,919
Chino found out
about you and Maria...

1524
02:19:07,171 --> 02:19:09,298
and he killed her.

1525
02:19:32,488 --> 02:19:34,406
Maria died?

1526
02:19:48,754 --> 02:19:51,590
Come and get me too, Chino!

1527
02:20:05,312 --> 02:20:07,815
Come and get me too, Chino!

1528
02:20:07,898 --> 02:20:09,900
- Who's that?
- lt's Anybodys. Come on.

1529
02:20:09,984 --> 02:20:11,902
Get out of here!

1530
02:20:13,112 --> 02:20:15,572
- Come and get me, damn you!
- What are ya doin'?

1531
02:20:15,656 --> 02:20:19,326
- Get out of here!
- Why don't you come with me--

1532
02:20:19,368 --> 02:20:21,912
lt ain't playin' anymore!
Can't any of you get that?

1533
02:20:21,996 --> 02:20:24,081
- But the gang!
- You're a girl!

1534
02:20:24,164 --> 02:20:26,125
Be a girl and beat it!

1535
02:20:32,881 --> 02:20:36,176
Come on, Chino!
Get me too!

1536
02:20:49,815 --> 02:20:52,484
Chino! l'm callin' for ya!

1537
02:20:53,986 --> 02:20:56,155
There's nobody here but me.

1538
02:20:56,196 --> 02:20:58,198
Come on!

1539
02:20:58,282 --> 02:21:00,326
Please, will ya?

1540
02:21:01,785 --> 02:21:04,288
l'm waitin' for ya.

1541
02:21:04,371 --> 02:21:06,290
l want you to.

1542
02:22:02,096 --> 02:22:05,015
l didn't believe hard enough.

1543
02:22:05,057 --> 02:22:07,434
Loving is enough.

1544
02:22:07,518 --> 02:22:11,855
Not here.
They won't let us be.

1545
02:22:12,690 --> 02:22:14,817
Then we'll get away.

1546
02:22:18,070 --> 02:22:20,906
- Yeah, we can.
- Yes.

1547
02:22:20,990 --> 02:22:23,283
- We will.
- Yes.

1548
02:22:24,368 --> 02:22:28,998
Hold my hand
and we're halfway there

1549
02:22:32,084 --> 02:22:38,382
Hold my hand
and l'll take you there

1550
02:22:38,424 --> 02:22:40,384
Somehow

1551
02:22:40,426 --> 02:22:42,553
Someday

1552
02:22:43,637 --> 02:22:45,264
Some--

1553
02:23:26,096 --> 02:23:27,431
Stay back!

1554
02:23:48,410 --> 02:23:51,372
How do you fire this gun, Chino?

1555
02:23:51,455 --> 02:23:53,040
Just by pulling
this little trigger?

1556
02:23:54,833 --> 02:23:57,920
How many bullets are left, Chino?

1557
02:23:58,003 --> 02:23:59,713
Enough for you?

1558
02:23:59,797 --> 02:24:01,507
And you?

1559
02:24:02,549 --> 02:24:03,967
All of you!

1560
02:24:04,051 --> 02:24:05,761
You all killed him.

1561
02:24:05,844 --> 02:24:08,347
And my brother.
And Riff.

1562
02:24:08,389 --> 02:24:10,975
Not with bullets and guns.

1563
02:24:11,058 --> 02:24:13,519
With hate!

1564
02:24:13,602 --> 02:24:17,648
Well, l can kill too,
because now l have hate!

1565
02:24:17,731 --> 02:24:19,692
How many can l kill, Chino?

1566
02:24:19,775 --> 02:24:23,612
How many, and still have
one bullet left for me?

1567
02:24:45,926 --> 02:24:48,178
Don't you touch him!


